config.author: AUT
config.visualStylePrompt: Siluetas sobre un fondo blanco plano. Sin degradados, sin sombras, sin texturas y sin contornos. Geometría: usa trazos gruesos y consistentes y simplificación geométrica. Todas las extremidades y terminales deben tener puntas redondeadas y vértices suavizados. Composición: representación plana 2D centrada. Usa el espacio negativo (blanco) para definir la separación interna entre formas negras superpuestas (por ejemplo, el espacio entre una cabeza y un torso). Claridad: maximiza la legibilidad y el reconocimiento semántico a escalas pequeñas. Evita cualquier rasgo facial o detalles intrincados. Usa color solo en el elemento distintivo, si es necesario.

nsm_explications.ID: SOMETHING SMALL. IT IS YOURS. WHEN OTHER PEOPLE SEE THIS THING, THEY CAN KNOW YOU.
nsm_explications.BRING: YOU MOVE TO HERE. AT THIS TIME, THIS THING IS NEAR YOU.

rows.prompt: The 'pictograma' is composed of a 'person' figure positioned on the left side of the frame. An 'arm' extends horizontally from the 'person' to the right, ending in a 'hand'. The 'hand' grasps a vertical, rectangular 'id_card' presented prominently in the foreground. Inside the 'id_card', a small 'photo_square' occupies the top corner, with horizontal 'text_lines' arranged below it to simulate text. A 'motion_arrow' is located beneath the 'arm', pointing from the 'person' toward the 'id_card', visually defining the action of bringing or presenting the document forward.

rows.UTTERANCE: I want to attend the celebration at the marae

nsm_explications.ATTEND_CELEBRATION_AT_MARAE: I WANT to be INSIDE this PLACE. MANY PEOPLE are HERE. SOMETHING GOOD HAPPEN HERE. I WANT to SEE this. I WANT to be NEAR these PEOPLE.

rows.prompt: The 'pictograma' is composed with a central, grounding perspective. The background is dominated by the large, triangular outline of the 'wharenui_structure', acting as a protective frame. The 'maihi_arms' extend downwards from the 'tekoteko_apex' to embrace the central space. Nestled securely within the base of the 'wharenui_structure' is the 'celebration_crowd', depicted as a dense, unified cluster of 'group_silhouettes'. In the lower foreground, separated by a span of negative space, stands the 'visitor_figure', slightly smaller than the building scale to emphasize humility. A visual 'trajectory_path' (implied or dotted) connects the 'visitor_figure' upwards toward the 'celebration_crowd', symbolizing the intention of movement and the desire to join the gathering.
